     H            Y.
     F** ALDR82 ********************************************
     F*   .. OUT-GOING TRACK DATA FILE REFORMATION ..      *
     F*       K.OKACHI                    2000.03.16       *
     F******************************************** ALDR82 **
     FALDPP20 IP  E                    DISK
     FALDWP82 O   E                    DISK
     F            ALDPP201                          KRENAMEALDWP821
     FALDWP83 O   E                    DISK
     F            ALDPP201                          KRENAMEALDWP831
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A1SHZ
     I                                        1   40A1SYYY
     I                                        5   60A1SYMM
     I                                        7   80A1SYDD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PHIZK   8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     MOVE PHIZK     WHIZK   80
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   70
      *
     C           A1SHZ     IFGT WHIZK
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   70
     C                     WRITEALDWP821
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEALDWP831
     C                     END
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
